{"tid":2211843,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD獲許可證向華為供貨","createTime":"2020-09-21T11:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T06:42:57.000Z","uid":241504,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"20de7e40a2ae0e0dd18bf1774bae201e4e52d55e","tid":2211843,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】中美科技戰越趨激化，但仍有美國公司嘗試在狹縫中跟華為做生意。科技資料網站Gizmochina報道，美國電腦處理器生產商AMD高級副總裁Forrest Norrod出席一個科技論壇表示，AMD取得向華為供貨的許可證，對陷入晶片斷供狀態的華為而言，帶來些微希望。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200920/ZEVMRNMGG5CMLMHEKOOU33KCNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200920%2FZEVMRNMGG5CMLMHEKOOU33KCNY%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZotUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=e5697410\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200920%2FZEVMRNMGG5CMLMHEKOOU33KCNY%2F&h=30192fa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200920/ZEVMRNMGG5CMLMHEKOOU33KCNY/</a>"},{"pid":"d9a4ffa39d88d81dda7c1f2d422bf4f78657cd0c","tid":2211843,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:14:44.000Z","msg":"出手救我地中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7f24bd06bdf0ed4c15febdf887761e127371c8","tid":2211843,"uid":145496,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"咩貨既許可證先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e44dccc2b2d27de8013bc148a248dc06abf9f3","tid":2211843,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f7f24bd06bdf0ed4c15febdf887761e127371c8","tid":2211843,"uid":145496,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:15:49.000Z","msg":"咩貨既許可證先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:20:03.000Z","msg":"處理器"},{"pid":"30f8f8d4520e1c281748735b4bbf3d2ae041f09a","tid":2211843,